content: You can view this agent and access its stored results, but creating new AI chats isn’t available for your current role. Ask your administrator or the agent owner to grant you permission if you need to start a chat.

comment.text: This text explains to users why they cannot start a new AI chat. It appears on a screen informing users about limited access, instructing them to contact an administrator or agent owner to request permission. This message clarifies the restriction and provides a solution.
